t=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Time, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. ἔτει</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in the last of many</tr_> years, i.e. after many years, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0435.tlg001:9\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cratin.Jun.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. χρόνῳ</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">after a very long</tr_> time, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg005.perseus-grc1:559\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pax\">Pax</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">559</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg024.perseus-grc1:196\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.196</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg057.perseus-grc1:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">57.18</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0541.tlg001:329\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Men.\">Men.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">329</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n84561.4\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in later Gr., <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">πολύς, πολλοστὸς ἔργοις</ref> </xr> one that has done <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a great deal,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0527.tlg012:23:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ LXX\">LXX</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ 2 Ki.\">2 Ki.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.20</b